title: Timothée Chalamet And Zendaya Take The BFF Test
author: BuzzFeed Celeb
description:
The power duo we always needed is finally here. Timothée Chalamet and Zendaya sat down to take the most chaotic BFF Test, like, ever. Who's Zendaya's celeb crush (!!!!!!) and what's Timmy's favorite curse word? Better watch and find out. And lemme just say that after this video, I’ve finally seen two pretty best friends.  #TimotheeChalamet #Zendaya #Dune
